init_text: An alien has kidnapped Matt Damon, not knowing what lengths humanity goes through to retrieve him whenever he goes missing.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The alien is unaware that Matt Damon is a famous actor and that his kidnapping is a huge deal.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The alien has a lot of questions for Matt Damon.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The alien is fascinated by the fact that Matt Damon is a human and that he is so different from him.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The people are very worried about him and they are trying to find him.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He decides to let Matt Damon go.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He told them how the alien had kidnapped him and how he was very nice to him.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The people were very happy that Matt Damon was safe and that the alien was not a threat to them.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He was very happy to be able to learn more about humans.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The alien was sad to say goodbye to Matt Damon and his friends.
